TI  - Relationships among vegetation, geomorphology and hydrology in the Bananal Island tropical wetlands, Araguaia River basin, Central Brazil
T2  - JOURNAL OF SOUTH AMERICAN EARTH SCIENCES
KW  - Bananal Island
