TI  - Can Eucalyptus invade native forest fragments close to commercial stands?
T2  - FOREST ECOLOGY AND MANAGEMENT
KW  - Eucalyptus
KW  - Natural regeneration
KW  - Seed germination
KW  - PINUS-RADIATA
KW  - REGENERATION
KW  - HERBIVORY
KW  - RECRUITMENT
KW  - COMPETITION
KW  - GLOBULUS
