TI  - Redefining identities, redefining landscapes: indigenous identity and land rights struggles in the Brazilian Amazon
T2  - JOURNAL OF CULTURAL GEOGRAPHY
KW  - Amazonia
KW  - indigenous
KW  - identity
KW  - landscape
KW  - conservation
